From cfffacc9a269d986eb3b66d131734424236a9e7c Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nanzhe Zhao <nzzhao@126.com>
Date: Mon, 22 Jun 2026 20:11:10 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 1/3] large folio + 16K alignment tracepoints + mmap align

- ext4: folio order cap sysfs (min/max_folio_order_cap)
- f2fs: folio order cap sysfs + large folio support
- mm: readahead_min_order sysfs
- mm: 16K alignment in generic_get_unmapped_area + tracepoints
- mm: huge_memory/khugepaged/madvise/vmscan large folio updates
- include: trace events for mmap unaligned + f2fs + huge_memory

NOTE: VMA boundary readahead patch (max_index) is NOT included;
it lives on feature/vma-readahead-bound branch only.

Change-Id: I346cb8800be948c8777fe5c4efe397b184747aaa
